# ============================================================================
# Summary of what IS included in GitHub:
# ✅ Source code (backend/app/, frontend/src/)
# ✅ Docker configs (Dockerfile, docker-compose.yml)
# ✅ Dependencies (requirements.txt, package.json)
# ✅ Documentation (docs/, *.md)
# ✅ Configuration (config/, alembic.ini)
# ✅ Deployment scripts (*.sh)
#
# ❌ NOT included (generated files):
# ❌ venv/, node_modules/ (~500+ MB)
# ❌ __pycache__/, dist/ (cache/build)
# ❌ .env files (secrets)
# ❌ logs/, *.db (runtime data)
# ============================================================================
